description: I’m the audience editor for The Times’s Culture desk. Here are five things I've been watching and listening to.
title: What’s in Our Queue? ‘Abbott Elementary’ and More
title_page: What’s in Our Queue? ‘Abbott Elementary’ and More - The New York Times
maintext:
What’s in Our Queue? ‘Abbott Elementary’ and More Maira Garcia In Brooklyn, looking for laughs ��
Instagram: @tikatheiggy
This Italian greyhound is one of the most fabulous dogs on social media.
Tika’s owners dress her up in extravagant outfits lined with tulle, fringe and feathers that look like they came off the runway.
Plus, the French Canadian accent they use to narrate her thoughts is nothing short of perfect.
See (and hear) it all for yourself.
